{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "死镇在夜间复活，灯火通明。绿袍老者（高师爷）勘查地形后告知铁大爷：七十二丈长街内有二十七个可供丝士藏身之处。铁大爷命三十七名死士出列，只留二十七人，六人因犹豫未拔刀被轿中暗器瞬间击杀。铁大爷为了保密，决定让多余的十人灭口。另一边，柳明秋向慕容解释'丝路'——它不是一条路，而是一个人，丝士们无他则无路可走。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "二十七。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "二十七?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "你真是看准了是二十七?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来，来人。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众骑士",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "有!",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二十七，",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要二十七。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有病的人，先退，有情愁纠缠的人，也退。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你们都想死在这里?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你们不如现在就去死吧!",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我已经把这个地方每一个角落都看过了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "这条街七十丈距离之内，最多只有二十七个藏身之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我的意思是说，只有这些蛇丝才能够在里面躲三天三夜的藏身之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "所以，也只有二十七个人能知道这二十七个藏身之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "现在我就要他们藏进去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "speaker_name": "绿袍老者",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "在你和慕容的决战日之前，他们的藏身处除了你我和他们二十七个人之外，绝不能被第二十八个人知道。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "这一点我当然也明白。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_gao_shi_ye",
      "text": "只可惜这一点如果只有我一个人明白，还是不够的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是不是也明白我们这位高师爷的意思呢?",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果你们都能了解高师爷的意思，那么现在你们应该知道怎么办。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "丝路，你是不是在说丝路?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "有丝，就有丝路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你说的那条丝路，是不是从汉时开辟，从盛唐通达，从长安始，经河西走廊，过嘉峪关，通黑水城，到达敦煌的那一条丝路?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "不是?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "丝路有两条，当然也是从长安始，由北走，出关，入哈密，吃哈密瓜，吃完哈密瓜后，就从通化、伊犁、阿尔泰山，一直走到我们所不知道的异国。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "这一条是北路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "去异国，带中土的丝绸去，返来时，带异国的奇巧珍玩、胡琴、胡床、碧眼美人来，这些可以在一趟行程中就获暴利的人，都把这条路叫作天山北路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "那么是不是还有一条天山南路?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "出关后，过高原，走西域、楼兰、莎车、沿疏勒走，而达目的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "在那些行旅客商的称呼中，这条路，就叫作天山南路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "不管天山南北路，都是丝路?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你说的是哪一条路?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "都不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳明秋",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我说的这条丝路，并不是一条路，而是一个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为这个人，在那些把自己的性命看作游丝般的'丝士'心目中，已经不是一个人，而是一条路，",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为没有他这个人，他们就无路可走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "所以这个人就叫作丝路?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "speaker_name": "柳先生",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "好，好极了。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "丝，丝路。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_liu_ming_qiu",
      "text": "你就算用西门吹雪的剑对准在我的咽喉上，我也想不出更好的名字了。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    }
  ],
